platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In Worms 4, shorter matches and streamlined menus crank up the pace, putting a bigger focus on the comical turn-based warfare. The game’s loaded with exciting ways to play: tackle tons of solo missions, join a faction and enter events, or battle other people in real-time contests locally or online. And it wouldn’t be a Worms game without exploding sheep and other classic weapons—or new ones like the fearsome Hayley’s Comet.
